name: 3B3-10 (V)
Lore: 'Infantry battle droid who assumed command after his regiment''s commander fell to Amidala''s blaster. Re-routed Droid Control Ship order to himself in the heat of battle.',
Text: 'While at an interior Naboo site, your [Presence] droids here are immune to We''ll Handle This and (if at opponent''s site) cannot be placed in Used Pile during battle. If with a unique (•) battle droid, draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise.',
